      <title>西班牙制药商 Grifols 董事长告诉报纸，将聘请独立董事</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/business/healthcare-pharmaceuticals/spanish-drug-maker-grifols-will-bring-independent-directors-chairman-tells-2024-04-14/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[西班牙制药商 Grifols 董事长在周日发表的报纸采访中表示，该公司正与今年股价暴跌作斗争，计划在其审计和薪酬委员会中增加独立董事，以改善其治理。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/business/healthcare-pharmaceuticals/spanish-drug-maker-grifols-will-bring-independent-directors-chairman-tells-2024-04-14/</guid>
