    <item>
      <title>佩雷拉击败希尔卫冕UFC轻重量级冠军</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/sports/pereira-knocks-out-hill-retain-ufc-light-heavyweight-title-2024-04-14/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[周六晚，巴西选手亚历克斯·佩雷拉在首轮淘汰赛中击败贾马哈·希尔，卫冕 UFC 轻重量级冠军，而张伟丽则在周六晚的 UFC 300 比赛中击败严晓楠，卫冕平量级腰带。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/sports/pereira-knocks-out-hill-retain-ufc-light-heavyweight-title-2024-04-14/</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 14 Apr 2024 06:04:31 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
